# --- User data (NEVER tracked publicly) ---
# All runtime state, diet/workout logs, foods, recipes, settings, exports
# live under DATA/ and stay on each user's own machine. Per the
# convention in CLAUDE.md, the app's data folder is gitignored by design.
DATA/
*.env

# --- Build artifacts (PyInstaller .exe is rebuilt locally; not versioned) ---
HealthTracker.exe
FitnessTracker.exe
build/
dist/
*.spec
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# --- Virtual environments ---
.venv/
venv/
env/

# --- Editor / OS / local tooling ---
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.code-workspace
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
